{
  "stem": "5644.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The people which we changed is the people which have been on the Christian side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Doesn't mean that I've been in organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could be private people smuggling in food to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But always we found them in the cemetery and boys who is staying here, the question--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--on the Christian side, and who is going back?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So in some cases, we said, no, we're going back because we've got to pick up something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're going back three of us, the same which came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they wait another day there at the cemetery hiding somewhere and waiting till someone-- because that was very often because we did have very many casualties during the ghetto time, people which died from hunger in there, it's all written over the world.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we've been going up very often to the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Which how many can you put on a cart?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Four, five people?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We did have hundreds.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did always have the three people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we did have some food which is smuggled in or things which you smuggled out to buy the food.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't have-- not in mine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I didn't hear about it, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't have to do that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He could dress himself and push the wagonette by giving some money to the men which was in charge of it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he didn't have to do-- but food in and things out had been easily smuggled, because the German didn't want to see it or touch it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was scared of typhus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We smuggled in guns for the organization.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We used it too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But mostly when we did deal-- dealt in guns and we dealt in ammunition or grenades or petrol, we always used one thing-- bribery.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
